v1.1.2 - events!

New Content:
+ Every 30 minutes, an event will trigger, giving every player a free boost. 
+ ALIEN INVASION!! A random event that drops up to 4 different unique items! Collect them around the map!

Balance Changes:
+ Enchant skip price now adjusts based on time remaining. (1m, 5m, 15m, 30m, 45m, 1h, 2h, 3h, 6h, 12h, 18h, 24h, 30h, 36h, 42h, 48h)
+ Added a description to the Ore Glazer, indicating that it removes the 'Neon' effect. [X]

Bug Fixes:
+ Computer with clocks set incorrectly can now see correct enchanting times (no longer using UTC time on the client).
+ Explosions no longer damage players, and now have a brand new look. [X]
+ Fixed a rare bug that caused loading to hang. This also fixes auto-rejoin occasionally breaking. [X]
+ Removed 1 precision decimals from item descriptions, and now all items use 2 decimal precision. [X]
+ Fixed a small issue with the base (mis-aligned parts) [X]
+ Ancient Scanner now acts like a real scanner, and the hitbox is fixed. [X]
+ Rebirth and Achievement items are now flagged as 'special' items, which means owning a Shiny Mythic will fill all index rewards below it (base, shiny, mythic). [X]
